		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Who we are?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Founded by two professionals each with 2 decades of IT Experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What is our team?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum Qualification – Bachelors in Engineering or Masters in the domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Totally 10 consultants with experience in various technologies and domains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Average Experience: 7+ years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on-resources Experience: 3+ years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-house trained&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are our strengths?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mobile Application development on Android platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web application development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web Design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shopping Cart Implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business Intelligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Database Remote/Onsite Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;System Administration Remote/Onsite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oracle Ebiz Offshore/OnSite Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Integration/Interfacing/ Migration/Conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are our modes of engagement?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location Engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ol style=&quot;list-style: none;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;– Onsite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;– Offshore&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Services Engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ol style=&quot;list-style: none;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;– Offshore / Onsite / Hybrid &amp;amp; Overlapping hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost Engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ol style=&quot;list-style: none;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;– Fixed Cost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;– Time and Material engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are our advantages?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost Effective&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly Experienced IT Professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rich Experience in Product Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Custom Application Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vast experience in serving international clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experts in providing Business Intelligence solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successful Support Engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast to embrace new and latest technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating and Adopting innovative ideas/methods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always looking for best Open Source Tools for better ROI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experts in Agile/Water fall Methodology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are our commitments?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outcome Certainty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Service and Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaboration with our Customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost Effective&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Best Practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled Professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are our Pricing Methods?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long term&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project Based&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Case-to-Case Basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;T&amp;amp;M&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fixed Cost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;24x7&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On-Call&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managed Services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are the remedies in case of a dispute?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do all possible to satisfy client within ambit of agreement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do find alternatives solutions by going out of way to provide solution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do the best to avoid disputes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However in case of dispute, resolve it through following approaches&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conciliation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mediation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Arbitration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ODR (Online Dispute Resolution).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are our Key-Differentiators?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operated by experts with decades of deep experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with a mission to provide fortune of services with minimum investment and low cost for the client&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product development on latest cutting edge technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Industry best practices adopted&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly skilled professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moden methods in Dispute Resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;center&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All the above at affordable cost&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/center&gt;</summary>
